  <brief_title>Use of Morphine Gel Topically in Patients With Stage 2-3 Wounds</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Single-Centered, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Efficacy and Safety Trial of Morphine Sulfate Gel 0.1% in Patients With Stage 2-3 Wounds</official_title>
  <sponsors>
